content:
The prebuilt data processing engine templates for insurance allow you to create datasets that improve sales and extend customer outreach.

You can customize the Data Processing Engine job templates or create a job template that suits your business needs. You can also schedule a template to run at defined intervals.

Customer Retention Offers: Use this template to get a list of customers with active policies and fewer than 10 claims in the last 10 years.
High-Value Customers: Use this template to get a list of accounts with a total premium over $100,000 a year.
Industry-Related Policies: Use this template to get a list of policies related to an industry.
Lapsed Policies: Use this template to get a list of lapsed insurance policies.
Life Event Updates: Use this template to get a list of customer life event updates for the last three months.
New Sales: Use this template to get a list of new sales that are pending quote to policy conversion.
Open Claims: Use this template to get a list of open claims.
Policy Renewals: Use this template to get a list of insurance policies up for renewal in the next 30 days.
title: Data Processing Engine Templates for Insurance
